{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-note-template-js","path":"/my first ring/","result":{"pageContext":{"id":"240f9a2b-f013-5faa-9121-120fcaa15398","html":"<h1>my first ring!</h1>\n<p>i signed up for a jewelry making class, and this was the first ring i made!</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/d3c45/first-ring-done.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"a ring with a twisted band and bezel setting\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/1c72d/first-ring-done.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/a80bd/first-ring-done.jpg 148w,\n/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/1c91a/first-ring-done.jpg 295w,\n/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/1c72d/first-ring-done.jpg 590w,\n/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/a8a14/first-ring-done.jpg 885w,\n/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/fbd2c/first-ring-done.jpg 1180w,\n/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/d3c45/first-ring-done.jpg 3472w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>this started as a piece of thick brass wire, which i bent into a twisted shape. that is done by clamping it in a vise, then using a steel bar to wind it until it's even.</p>\n<p>then it goes through a roller to flatten it.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a048288fc72ba6d1bd9e0058953136cb/d3c45/first-ring-band-flat.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"a ring band made of twisted metal\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/a048288fc72ba6d1bd9e0058953136cb/1c72d/first-ring-band-flat.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a048288fc72ba6d1bd9e0058953136cb/a80bd/first-ring-band-flat.jpg 148w,\n/static/a048288fc72ba6d1bd9e0058953136cb/1c91a/first-ring-band-flat.jpg 295w,\n/static/a048288fc72ba6d1bd9e0058953136cb/1c72d/first-ring-band-flat.jpg 590w,\n/static/a048288fc72ba6d1bd9e0058953136cb/a8a14/first-ring-band-flat.jpg 885w,\n/static/a048288fc72ba6d1bd9e0058953136cb/fbd2c/first-ring-band-flat.jpg 1180w,\n/static/a048288fc72ba6d1bd9e0058953136cb/d3c45/first-ring-band-flat.jpg 3472w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>then we did the bezel setting, which involved cutting a flat strip of brass to fit around the stone, then soldering it to a back plate.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/767031f5408b4f045673e52792fddd63/d3c45/first-ring-bezel-wip.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"a tigers eye stone with a strip of brass around it\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/767031f5408b4f045673e52792fddd63/1c72d/first-ring-bezel-wip.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/767031f5408b4f045673e52792fddd63/a80bd/first-ring-bezel-wip.jpg 148w,\n/static/767031f5408b4f045673e52792fddd63/1c91a/first-ring-bezel-wip.jpg 295w,\n/static/767031f5408b4f045673e52792fddd63/1c72d/first-ring-bezel-wip.jpg 590w,\n/static/767031f5408b4f045673e52792fddd63/a8a14/first-ring-bezel-wip.jpg 885w,\n/static/767031f5408b4f045673e52792fddd63/fbd2c/first-ring-bezel-wip.jpg 1180w,\n/static/767031f5408b4f045673e52792fddd63/d3c45/first-ring-bezel-wip.jpg 3472w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>this is then soldered (without the stone) to the band, which just requires a little bit of filing. it is a little tricky to make sure that this part lines up right.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/46b3046305006edc084b985632cd8337/d3c45/first-ring-stone-set-wip.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"a brass ring with a bezel set on top\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/46b3046305006edc084b985632cd8337/1c72d/first-ring-stone-set-wip.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/46b3046305006edc084b985632cd8337/a80bd/first-ring-stone-set-wip.jpg 148w,\n/static/46b3046305006edc084b985632cd8337/1c91a/first-ring-stone-set-wip.jpg 295w,\n/static/46b3046305006edc084b985632cd8337/1c72d/first-ring-stone-set-wip.jpg 590w,\n/static/46b3046305006edc084b985632cd8337/a8a14/first-ring-stone-set-wip.jpg 885w,\n/static/46b3046305006edc084b985632cd8337/fbd2c/first-ring-stone-set-wip.jpg 1180w,\n/static/46b3046305006edc084b985632cd8337/d3c45/first-ring-stone-set-wip.jpg 3472w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>from there it just needs a polish and setting! setting is not super hard, but requires a careful hammering around the edge to ensure the stone is secure.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/345c4c82cd2130b8c4073f81a242d250/d3c45/first-ring-polished.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"a ring polished but without a stone in the setting\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/345c4c82cd2130b8c4073f81a242d250/1c72d/first-ring-polished.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/345c4c82cd2130b8c4073f81a242d250/a80bd/first-ring-polished.jpg 148w,\n/static/345c4c82cd2130b8c4073f81a242d250/1c91a/first-ring-polished.jpg 295w,\n/static/345c4c82cd2130b8c4073f81a242d250/1c72d/first-ring-polished.jpg 590w,\n/static/345c4c82cd2130b8c4073f81a242d250/a8a14/first-ring-polished.jpg 885w,\n/static/345c4c82cd2130b8c4073f81a242d250/fbd2c/first-ring-polished.jpg 1180w,\n/static/345c4c82cd2130b8c4073f81a242d250/d3c45/first-ring-polished.jpg 3472w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>all done!</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/d3c45/first-ring-done.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"a brass ring with a twisted wire band and bezel-set tigers eye\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/1c72d/first-ring-done.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/a80bd/first-ring-done.jpg 148w,\n/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/1c91a/first-ring-done.jpg 295w,\n/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/1c72d/first-ring-done.jpg 590w,\n/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/a8a14/first-ring-done.jpg 885w,\n/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/fbd2c/first-ring-done.jpg 1180w,\n/static/826646a3cfd5f7a8148acfde4a3b6f2b/d3c45/first-ring-done.jpg 3472w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}